            Temporal analysis builds a yield prediction model that gets more
            accurate with each data collection. Make confident harvest planning
            and marketing decisions backed by field-level intelligence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="yield-chart-wrap reveal">
          <div class="yield-chart" aria-label="Yield forecast accuracy chart showing improvement over growing season" role="img">
            <div class="yield-y-axis" aria-hidden="true">
